{"word":"G283 - ἀμίαντος - amíantos - am-ee'-an-tos - Undefiled","slug":"G283","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀμίαντος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>amíantos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>am-ee'-an-tos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Undefiled"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B1;&#x03BD;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - amiantos</b> - <i>am-ee'-an-tos</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3392\">G3392</a>; <i>unsoiled</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>pure:</i> - undefiled."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3392\">G3392</a>, <a href=\"#/G3393\">G3393</a>, <a href=\"#/G3394\">G3394</a>"}]}